  "id": "RAW_613199c6",
  "title": "一个人，运营一家跨境公司，我用阿里这款 AI 智能体实现了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MTQ4NjQzMw==&mid=2652794713&idx=1&sn=ae86dcf9a7cbac2ce843652513c342f9",
  "date": "2025-12-29 10:04:00",
  "author": "智东西",
  "siteName": "智东西",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0275dc93&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiajPiaWCelW6Jic1LjLMzAJ311Apy67ekAzMV8Hr5tl8KU9vOH7KetUdG48A556vQibxDwpL5jPUiakmA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">▲图片由AI生成</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI推动“中国制造”一键批发到全球。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">李水青</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">漠影</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一位亚马逊卖家向AI输入了这样一句话：“情人节礼物有哪些蓝海市场？给我推荐一些可以卖的商品。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">几分钟后，他收到了一份完整的解决方案：</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">从市场分析与品类推荐，到符合市场需求的设计图，再到精准匹配的、支持小单定制和一件代发的东莞制造商名单，一键询盘获得行情信息甚至自动下单。整个过程，他只需要提出想法和检查成果，体验如同开上了“智驾”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.687037037037037\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3a647775&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiajPiaWCelW6Jic1LjLMzAJ31FtAcDxJj4Def2f6uRUS2ibxl7jlxIDYvkF9U023c4Dob4CXnVKzSdkA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲亚马逊卖家向AI寻求生意建议</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是阿里旗下源头厂货平台1688最近上线的</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">跨境AI智能体“遨虾”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">展示的能力。与市面上众多“玩具型”AI不同，它将自己定位成“</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">生产力工具</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">据悉，近日“遨虾”还超过ChatGPT ，登顶了通义实验室的一个大模型榜单。该榜单全面衡量智能体在电商环境下的实际能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“遨虾”的研发团队自称是“用盖大楼的钱来盖一个小卖部”——以</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">千卡级算力投入到垂直领域</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，在复杂的跨境贸易中实现AI深度降本增效。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">跨境贸易是否真的迎来“智能驾驶”的拐点？</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">智东西第一时间参与了“遨虾”的内测和公测体验，并与1688跨境业务负责人和“遨虾”产品负责人进行了深度访谈，试图为大家呈现AI大模型在中国制造产业链中的落地真相。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">万亿跨境生意</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">两大商业困境</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">跨境生意蕴藏着万亿级的市场机会，但其高门槛却将无数中小卖家拒之门外。这些困境，归根结底源于</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">两大商业本质难题：信息不对称与边际成本。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">商业跟用不用大模型没关系。</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">它的困难永远都是两方面：一个是成本与效率，另外就是信息对称。”1688跨境总经理一隆说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">信息不对称让跨境选品如同赌博。</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">一隆举了一个生动的例子，比如一个国内卖家要把夏天穿的短袖卖到美国，3月份就要发货，1月份就要提前生产好，这意味着要提前半年预测一个陌生群体的喜好；相比之下，内贸做一个爆款可能只要几周就把开款、打样、生产、上架、销售全做完了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-w=\"500\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b75821b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiajPiaWCelW6Jic1LjLMzAJ31IswoziaZsMIchIAWN0V1x7puxBuUgzsialEpD5CNPsKaSxoboB6GECSA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲从中国卖向国外的服饰产品</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">同时，规模瓶颈则制约着小卖家的生长。</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">不同国家国情不同，一套市场信息和方案难以通用。一个小卖家往往只能聚焦一个跨境电商平台以及一两个国家市场，难以形成规模效应。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“遨虾”试图攻克的，正是这两个商业难题。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">在信息不对称方面，</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">“遨虾”汇聚了1688及阿里生态内独特的、实时更新的供需数据。“阿里对商业网络供需侧的数据整体覆盖是最全面的。”一隆说。这使卖家能从中获得真正指导行动的商业洞察，并精准匹配工厂，“大概可以达到前20%的人类买手的水准”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">在成本重构方面，</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">“遨虾”通过AI一键完成多国家多平台智能选品、多语言翻译、多工厂自动询盘、素材生成等，试图将跨境运营的边际成本打到“理论最低值”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5175925925925926\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=439855a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiajPiaWCelW6Jic1LjLMzAJ31hoRw2FNicQ0cJdS4Gek8dXrJ2lHNeR0TLd2AIXDkJSabWvpyNz8hSow%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲“遨虾”生成的素材案例展示</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能“副驾”时代：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个人，就是一家跨境公司？</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在试用过程中，令智东西感受最深刻的是，不同于市面上散点式的AI应用产品，这款AI智能体</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">罕见地覆盖了一条超长的工作流：</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">智能选品、选商，到素材创作，到自动询盘、咨询</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，一环扣一环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4462962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=64c99529&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiajPiaWCelW6Jic1LjLMzAJ318zMFqF3NBYHTsbN44OgN1bIhhnzYa6uTdALAVGz5qRxTLic6L9t72UA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲多个工作流节点环环相扣</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">1、智能选品选商：一个想法输出深度报告，“红海”还是“蓝海”一目了然</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当我输入“帮美国大学生找宿舍用迷你洗衣机”的需求后，系统不仅提供了市场竞争度分析、价格区间等量化维度，还精准匹配了多家广东揭阳小家电工厂。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“遨虾”首先会基于提问，选择调用多个智能体进行需求理解、商品筛选、用户分析、市场分析等，耗时在1-2分钟之间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1212962962962962\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1cd61e80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLiajPiaWCelW6Jic1LjLMzAJ31Gb7HQsp0XbYXeoBRTAhHDia32iawV7MGibJhYw4iaCSUdSYlIYACcbGiakQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲“遨虾”生成的深度报告部分截图</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">紧接着，其输出一份“美国大学生宿舍迷你洗衣机的选品报告”，如下图所示，该报告“强烈建议优先布局充电式内衣洗衣机赛道”。报告第一部分从“需求理解和选品逻辑”说起，明确了“高增长、低竞争、强场景适配”的选品逻辑，思路清晰明确。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505311011\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35361216730038025\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1052\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/z7ZD1WagSLgjEFqUr9y3Lm1VZRRSoRcIDmUEDtzkiaiclLiblScfzITakYqYEkIuJar03RfaqvgysgaoaYujueXZg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"418\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e545af48&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgjEFqUr9y3Lm1VZRRSoRcIDmUEDtzkiaiclLiblScfzITakYqYEkIuJar03RfaqvgysgaoaYujueXZg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲“遨虾”生成的深度报告部分截图</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在报告第二部分，“遨虾”进行了市场扫描与机会确认，发现某充电式内衣洗衣机“近三个月月销量从176飙升到1040”，而“品牌垄断了仅26%”，因此判断这一市场相比手动便捷式洗衣机处于爆发初期，是“绝佳的蓝海入局机会”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6083333333333333\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestbl